abstract: The news channel, which replaced Current TV on Tuesday, lost some viewers when it was dropped by AT&T U-verse and could not be streamed over the Internet.
snippet: The news channel, which replaced Current TV on Tuesday, lost some viewers when it was dropped by AT&T U-verse and could not be streamed over the Internet.
lead_paragraph: There was ample attention in journalistic circles as Al Jazeera America had its premiere on Tuesday — particularly among those who could not watch.

headline.main: Al Jazeera Makes Limited American Debut
headline.print_headline: Hiccup for Debut of Al Jazeera America
